title: Former garda accused of manslaughter to be extradited to UK after image appeared on Crimecall
text: Former garda accused of manslaughter to be extradited to UK after image appeared on Crimecall Independent.ie The High Court has ordered the extradition of a former Garda to the UK on an alleged manslaughter charge after he handed himself in to gardai following his image appearing on RTE's Crimecall programme. http://www.independent.ie/irish-news/courts/former-garda-accused-of-manslaughter-to-be-extradited-to-uk-after-image-appeared-on-crimecall-35363115.html http://www.independent.ie/incoming/article35165877.ece/1aa6f/AUTOCROP/h342/Crimecall.jpg Keelin Shanley on RTÃ‰ Crimecall and inset Oliver Hurley The High Court has ordered the extradition of a former Garda to the UK on an alleged manslaughter charge after he handed himself in to gardai following his image appearing on RTE's Crimecall programme.
